# Chrome extension signing key (pins the unpacked extension's ID; keep local-only).
# Deliberately NOT under ai-prompt-extension/ — Chrome's "Load unpacked" scans that whole
# folder and warns about bundled .pem/.key files (a real packaging hazard if ever zipped).
chrome-signing-key.pem
